<blockquote>
  <p>At the top it said “my seizure plan”. I blinked at it then looked up at her. “Are you having a seizure now?” I asked. “No, but I’m about to.” She looked down at the monitor on her finger. “Can you sit with me until your stop?” She asked.</p>
</blockquote>

<p>A heart-wrenching slice of life story about this girl living with a disability, doing the best she can, just trying to get through the day.</p>
